    "After teaching the entire AI sequence, the students' learning progress was assessed through a test.",
    "Furthermore, we conducted semistructured interviews with the teachers.",
    "The data was analyzed qualitatively using an inductive approach in line with grounded theory, triangulating the different data sources.",
    "In addition to general barriers in line with existing literature, such as issues with mathematical and programming skills, we identified several AI/ML-specific learning difficulties.",
    "First, our results suggest that students have difficulties in evaluating whether certain AI/ML methods can be applied to a given problem."
